quran[30]{c,v,t,f}:
  68,40,"Bi wọ́n léèrè wò pé èwo nínú wọn l’ó lè fọwọ́ ìyẹn sọ̀yà!"
  68,41,"Tàbí wọ́n ní (àwọn òrìṣà kan) tí wọ́n jẹ́ akẹgbẹ́ Wa? Kí wọ́n mú àwọn òrìṣà wọn wá nígbà náà tí wọ́n bá jẹ́ olódodo."
  68,42,"Ní ọjọ́ tí A máa ṣí ojúgun sílẹ̀, A sì máa pè wọ́n síbi ìforíkanlẹ̀, wọn kò sì níí lè ṣe é."
  69,37,"Kò sí ẹni tí ó máa jẹ ẹ́ bí kò ṣe àwọn ẹlẹ́ṣẹ̀."
  69,38,"Nítorí náà, Èmi ń fi ohun tí ẹ̀ ń fojú rí búra"
  69,39,"àti ohun tí ẹ ò fojú rí."
  70,31,"nítorí náà, ẹnikẹ́ni tó bá ń wá n̄ǹkan mìíràn lẹ́yìn ìyẹn, àwọn wọ̀nyẹn gan-an ni olùtayọ-ẹnu ààlà;"
  70,32,"àwọn tó ń ṣọ́ àgbàfipamọ́ wọn àti àdéhùn wọn;"
  70,33,"àwọn tó ń dúró ti ìjẹ́rìí (òdodo) wọn;"
  71,28,"Olúwa mi foríjìn èmi, àwọn òbí mi méjèèjì àti ẹni tó bá wọ inú ilé mi (tí ó jẹ́) onígbàgbọ́ òdodo àti àwọn onígbàgbọ́ òdodo lọ́kùnrin àti onígbàgbọ́ òdodo lóbìnrin. Má sì ṣàlékún kan fún àwọn alábòsí àfi ìparun.”"
  72,25,"Sọ pé: “Èmi kò mọ̀ bóyá ohun tí Wọ́n ń ṣe ní àdéhùn fún yín ti súnmọ́ tàbí Olúwa mi yóò fún un ní àkókò tó jìnnà."
  72,26,"Onímọ̀-ìkọ̀kọ̀, kò sì fi (ìmọ̀) ìkọ̀kọ̀ Rẹ̀ han ẹnì kan"
  72,27,"àyàfi ẹni tí Ó ṣàlẹ́ṣà tí ó jẹ́ Òjísẹ́.{1} Dájúdájú Ó ń mú ẹ̀ṣọ́ kan rìn níwájú Òjíṣẹ́ náà àti lẹ́yìn rẹ̀.",footnotes:1:[Ànábì Muhammad - kí ìkẹ́ àti ọlà Allāhu máa bá a - ni òpin àwọn Ànábì àti òpin àwọn Òjíṣẹ́ Ọlọ́hun. Kò sí àáfà kan kan tí Allāhu ń fi iṣẹ́ ìmísí rán mọ́. aṣ-Ṣaetọ̄n àlùjànnú ni àwọn àáfà tó ń woṣẹ́ bá dòwò pọ̀. Òjíṣẹ́ àlùjànnú ni irú wọn, wọn kì í ṣe “òjíṣẹ́ Ọlọ́hun”.]
  73,19,"Dájúdájú èyí ni ìrántí. Nítorí náà, ẹni tí ó bá fẹ́ kí ó mú ojú ọ̀nà kan tọ̀ dé ọ̀dọ̀ Olúwa rẹ̀."
  73,20,"Dájúdájú Olúwa rẹ mọ̀ pé dájúdájú ìwọ ń dìde kírun fún ohun tó kéré sí ìlàta méjì òru tàbí ìlàjì rẹ̀ tàbí ìlàta rẹ̀. Igun kan nínú àwọn tó wà pẹ̀lú rẹ (náà ń ṣe bẹ́ẹ̀). Allāhu l’Ó ń ṣòdíwọ̀n òru àti ọ̀sán. Ó sì mọ̀ pé ẹ kò lè ṣọ́ ọ.1 Nítorí náà, Ó ti dá a padà sí fífúyẹ́ fún yín. Nítorí náà, ẹ ké ohun tí ó bá rọrùn (fún yín) nínú al-Ƙur’ān. Ó mọ̀ pé àwọn aláìsàn yóò wà nínú yín. Àwọn mìíràn sì ń rìrìn àjò lórí-ilẹ̀, tí wọ́n ń wá nínú oore Allāhu. Àwọn mìíràn sì ń jagun sí ojú-ọ̀nà Allāhu. Nítorí náà, ẹ ké ohun tí ó bá rọrùn (fún yín) nínú rẹ̀. Ẹ kírun (ọ̀ran-an-yàn). Ẹ yọ Zakāh. Kí ẹ sì yá Allāhu ní dúkìá tó dára. Ohunkóhun tí ẹ bá tì síwájú fún ẹ̀mí ara yín nínú ohun rere, ẹ̀yin yóò bá a lọ́dọ̀ Allāhu ní ohun rere àti ní ohun tí ó tóbi jùlọ ní ẹ̀san. Ẹ tọrọ àforíjìn lọ́dọ̀ Allāhu. Dájúdájú Allāhu ni Aláforíjìn, Àṣàkẹ́-ọ̀run.{1}.",footnotes:1:[Ìṣọ́-òru jẹ́ iṣẹ́ tí ẹ̀dá kò lágbára láti ṣe. Ìṣọ́-òru ni kí ẹ̀dá lérò pé òun kò níí fojú kan oorun láti alẹ́ mọ́júmọ́ lójojúmọ́.]
  74,16,"Rárá o! Dájúdájú ó jẹ́ alátakò sí àwọn āyah Wa."
  74,17,"Èmi yóò la ìyà pọ́nkèpọ́nkè bọ̀ ọ́ lọ́rùn (nínú Iná){1}..",footnotes:1:[Orúkọ àpáta ńlá kan nínú Iná ni Sọ‘ūd. Kèfèrí yóò máa pọ́n òkè náà láààrin àádọ́rin ọdún ní àpọ́njábọ́. Ìdí nìyí tí wọ́n fi pe ìyà náà ní ìyà pọ́nkèpọ́nkè.]
  74,18,"Dájúdájú ó ronú (lódì nípa al-Ƙur’ān). Ó sì pinnu (ọ̀rọ̀ kan nínú ẹ̀mí rẹ̀)."
  75,13,"Wọ́n máa fún ènìyàn ní ìró ní ọjọ́ yẹn nípa ohun tó tì síwájú (nínú iṣẹ́ rẹ̀) àti ohun tó fi kẹ́yìn (nínú orípa iṣẹ́ rẹ̀)."
  75,14,"Ṣebí ènìyàn dá ara rẹ̀ mọ̀,"
  75,15,"ìbáà mú àwọn àwáwí rẹ̀ wá."
  76,7,"Wọ́n ń mú ẹ̀jẹ́ wọn ṣẹ. Wọ́n sì ń páyà ọjọ́ kan, tí aburú rẹ̀ jẹ́ ohun tí ó máa fọ́nká gan-an."
  76,8,"Tòhun ti bí wọ́n ṣe ní ìfẹ́ sí (ọrọ̀ tó), wọ́n ń fún mẹ̀kúnnù, ọmọ òrukàn àti ẹrú ní oúnjẹ jẹ."
  76,9,"(Wọ́n sì ń sọ pé:) “Nítorí Ojú rere Allāhu (nìkan) l’a fi ń fun yín ní oúnjẹ jẹ; àwa kò sì gbèrò ẹ̀san tàbí ìdúpẹ́ kan láti ọ̀dọ̀ yín."
  77,4,"Ó fi àwọn tó ń ṣèpínyà láààrin òdodo àti irọ́ búra."
  77,5,"Ó fi àwọn mọlāika tó ń mú ìrántí wá (bá àwọn Òjíṣẹ́) búra."
  77,6,"(Ìrántí náà jẹ́) àwíjàre tàbí ìkìlọ̀."
  78,1,"Nípa kí ni wọ́n ń bíra wọn léèrè ná?"
  78,2,"Nípa ìró ìkọ̀kọ̀ ńlá ni,"
  78,3,"èyí tí wọ́n ń yapa-ẹnu lórí rẹ̀."